Ellis bụ onye edemede a ma ama nke akwụkwọ kọmputa.

Ellis nwetara nzere masta nke sayensị na sayensị kọmputa na Mahadum California. Obụ onye na-ede akwụkwọ nke The Annotated C++ Reference Manual, ya na Bjarne Stroustrup.O sokwa dee Designing and Coding Reusable C++ ya na Martin D
Carroll na afo (1995).Ọ rụrụ ọrụ maka AT&T Bell Laboratories, UNIX System Laboratories, na Novell na mmepe nchịkọta.
